title: Hour 1 - 49ers Can Make Super Bowl, Contentious Press Conferences
itunes:title: Hour 1 - 49ers Can Make Super Bowl, Contentious Press Conferences
description:
Dan reacts to the Jimmy Garoppolo led San Francisco 49ers win over the Los Angeles Rams on Monday Night Football. And he also weighs in on the contentious press conference response from Nick Saban as Alabama is preparing to face Jimbo Fisher and Texas A&M this weekend.
